"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-15-nnpp-chieftain-decries-nigerias-performance-at-paris-olympic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  A chieftain of the New Nigeria People's Party, NNPP, Olufemi Ajadi Oguntoyinbo has described the over N12bn spent at the 2024 Paris Olympics competition as a 'wastage'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He decried the failure of Nigeria's contingent at the just concluded games and their failure to clinch any medals despite the huge financial commitment by the government.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DAILY POST gathered that Nigeria fielded 88 athletes in 12 sports in Paris and ended up without a medal.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5663276047428435e-14, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999394174215669, \"rank\": 6.058624890663427e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NNPP chieftain in his reaction, said the amount that was invested is painful because there were no results to show for it.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that it is almost two times the amount of the country's entire budget for the Ministry of Science and Technology this year.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oguntoyinbo in a statement made available to DAILY POST on Thursday, then called on the Federal government to probe the cause of this wastage and failure.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5663276047428435e-14, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He urged the Federal government to focus more on Science and Technology development as they are doing on sports.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The NNPP chieftain said, \\\"We fielded 88 athletes in 12 sports with 12bn in Paris and ended up without a medal, this is over N136 million (about $85,000) spent on each of the 88 Nigerian contingents to the Olympics, and no singular medal was won.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999394174215669, \"rank\": 6.058624890663427e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.981329326245497, \"rank\": 0.019025900128781012, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While Jamaica, a nation which spent far less than we did, a total of about $2300 on each contingent, won 6 medals; 1 Gold, 3 Silver and 2 Bronze at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999844706488429, \"rank\": 1.509123676951854e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We must now question how we made this huge investment, without getting any returns.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that the Paris Olympics 2024 has officially ended and Team Nigeria, despite the huge financial investment made into the project, returned without a single medal amounts to wastage.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let me call on the Federal Government to institute a probe into the performance of our 88 contingent to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.5566622663148296, \"rank\": 0.7905638863514632, \"text\": \"Federal Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to register my displeasure with the recklessness and shoddy preparation for the Olympics leading to a wastage of over N12bn.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasting this amount under our present state of the economy is something we cannot sweep under the carpet\\\".\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alade joins Ikorodu City from 1472 FC  Barcelona winger, Lamine Yamal's father out of danger after multiple stabs  NNPP urges INEC to comply with court order recognising Major-led NWC  Kano APC gives NNPP 72 hours  to retract allegations of influencing judiciary  NNPP faction vows to appeal court ruling that affirmed Agbo Major as national chairman  Kwankwaso-Led NNPP declares court judgment miscarriage of justice  Kwankwaso behind litigations in NNPP, not APC - National Secretary  NNPP condemns attack on its members in Kano  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ikorodu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ikorodu\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ikorodu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ikorodu\"}, {\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"score\": 0.9771081808450498, \"rank\": 0.02337423474875871, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\", \"score\": 0.9999999990254764, \"rank\": 9.745791430487305e-10, \"text\": \"Yamal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\"}, {\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_West_Company\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NWC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_West_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_West_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.054608416500822e-16, \"text\": \"Kano\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\"}, {\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.047887975777898e-31, \"text\": \"APC\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.047887975777898e-31, \"text\": \"APC\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Progressives_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.054608416500822e-16, \"text\": \"Kano\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kano_State\"}]}]}"